    <item>
      <title>前外汇主管称干预是日元过度疲软的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/former-fx-chief-says-intervention-an-option-for-overly-weak-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前货币主管表示，干预是解决日元过度疲软问题的选择之一，他在美国通胀数据公布之前发表讲话，该数据可能会推动日元突破市场参与者密切关注的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/former-fx-chief-says-intervention-an-option-for-overly-weak-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲投资银行将在西班牙支持 10 亿欧元风险投资基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/european-investment-bank-to-back-1-billion-vc-fund-in-spain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲投资银行的风险投资部门将支持西班牙的一个新基金，该基金旨在向成长阶段的科技初创企业投资 10 亿欧元（11 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/european-investment-bank-to-back-1-billion-vc-fund-in-spain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于持续的风险，明年欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/european-gas-prices-through-next-year-rise-on-persistent-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气小幅走高，由于供应风险（包括来自俄罗斯的剩余流量）持续存在不确定性，预计明年冬季燃料价格将更加昂贵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/european-gas-prices-through-next-year-rise-on-persistent-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管竞争对手因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎，宝马电动汽车销量仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马公司其核心品牌的全电动汽车销量在第一季度大幅增长，表现优于竞争对手特斯拉和梅赛德斯奔驰，后者一直在努力应对疲软的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
